name: EROS
description: This artwork presents solid abstract lines that depict the roughness of the beginning of any sexual journey, to the vibrant choice of color palette that captures the melting down of one's own mind & body - feeling every inch of emotion and letting go of that sense of control, leading to the almost godlike feeling of climax through the highlights and shadows making a luscious and eye candy piece. Some may interpret the artwork as a sexual awakening or a spiritual rediscovery but one thing anyone can be sure of - it is that perfect little moment between chaos and harmony. The artwork can stand alone even with just the linework, the colors, or the high lights & shadows but just like in any sexual encounter, it is best experienced with a full course.
